tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ElectionResults (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    candidate_name VARCHAR(255),
    party_affiliation VARCHAR(255),
    votes_received INT,
    election_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE PollingCenters (
    center_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    center_name VARCHAR(255),
    location VARCHAR(255),
    start_time TIME,
    end_time TIME
);

CREATE TABLE VoterRecords (
    voter_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    voter_name VARCHAR(255),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    registered_center_id INT
);
